Collections.comment: Create subclasses about the grocery items, complete with the description and product's picture
Collections.rule:
Class: @A*
   SubClassOf: GroceryItem, containsFoodStuff some @B*
   Annotations: rdfs:comment @C*(xml:lang="en"),
                foaf:depiction @D*(IRI)

Collections.comment: Create a simple class hierarchy about how the food stuff is organized
Create individuals about the nutrition facts of each food stuff
Collections.rule:
Individual: @A*(mm:hashEncode)
   Types: NutritionalInformation
   Facts: productName @A*,
          hasTotalFat @B*(xsd:decimal mm:decimalFormat("##0.00")),
          hasSaturatedFat @C*(xsd:decimal mm:decimalFormat("##0.00")),
          hasSugar @I*(xsd:integer),
          hasSodium @F*(xsd:integer mm:capturing("([0-9]+)"))

Collections.comment: Create subclasses that define the food stuff based on its ingredient components
